cmput301w15t07.TravelTracker.model

Class Destination

  • java.lang.Object
    • cmput301w15t07.TravelTracker.model.Destination

  • public class Destination
extends Object
    Model object for Claim Destinations. Setters are not exposed - object attributes are set at construction time. This is so that mutations must be made at the Claim for observer notification and cache dirtying.
    Author:
    kdbanman
